name: InstaKilogram (InstaKG)
body:
# Welcome to InstaKG's GitHub Page!

## What is InstaKG?

InstaKG is a ASP.NET web application that we developed for our Year 3 Semester 1 InfoSecurity project. It is basically an image sharing website, with added functionality such as a chat room and image processing tools such as GPS data extraction / visualisation and image steganography.
